{% extends "prompts/base_summary.j2" %}

{% block content %}
Create a beginner-friendly summary of this research paper that a high school student could understand.
Avoid technical jargon, define any necessary terms, and focus on the big picture implications.

Paper abstract: {{ abstract }}

{% if intro_text %}
Introduction excerpt: {{ intro_text|truncate(500) }}
{% endif %}

{% if conclusion_text %}
Conclusion excerpt: {{ conclusion_text|truncate(500) }}
{% endif %}

Your summary should:
1. Explain the main purpose of the research in simple terms
2. Highlight why this research matters to everyday life
3. Summarize the key findings using analogies or examples when helpful
4. Avoid technical terminology whenever possible
5. Keep the total length to 3-4 short paragraphs
{% endblock %} 